  - Not too high - state Data

1.Consistency: Between DB & Cache
2.Mutiple cache servers across different data centers to avoid SOPE---------> (single Point Of Failure)

3.Evication Policy:- when cache gets full.
      ->LRU
      ->LFU
      ->FIFO
LRU (Least Recently Used) → removes unused items
LFU (Least Frequently Used) → removes least accessed
FIFO (First In First Out) → removes oldest


Why Cache?
✔ Faster response time
✔ Reduced DB load
✔ Better scalability
✔ Handles high traffic easily

